  "prompt": "What are sticker packs in criminal case and how are they useful in the game?",
  "response": "In the mobile game \"Criminal Case,\" sticker packs are collectible items that players can gather as they progress through the game. These packs typically feature various stickers that reflect themes or characters related to the game\u2019s storyline and cases. \n\n### Uses of Sticker Packs in Criminal Case:\n1. **Game Progression**: Collecting stickers can sometimes unlock additional content, such as new cases or levels. \n2. **Social Interaction**: Players may share or trade stickers with friends, enhancing the social aspect of the game.\n3. **Customization**: Stickers can often be used to decorate a player\u2019s profile or showcase accomplishments within the game.\n4. **Achievements and Challenges**: Collecting specific sticker packs might help players complete challenges or earn achievements, providing motivation to explore more aspects of the game.\n5. **Aesthetic Appeal**: Collectible stickers can add fun and personalization to the gameplay experience, allowing players to express themselves through their collections.\n\nOverall, sticker packs add an engaging layer to \"Criminal Case,\" incentivizing exploration and social interaction while enhancing the gameplay experience.",
